title: TUESDAY 3/2 -JJ Watt has a new home
itunes:title: TUESDAY 3/2 -JJ Watt has a new home
description:
JJ Watt joining his former teammate, DeAndre Hopkins in the Arizona as he signs with the Cardinals (0:08). Chiefs general manager Brett Veach gives a status update on Patrick Mahomes and his injured toe (1:46) as well as plans to upgrade the offensive line (2:08). Plus, Alex Smith expected to hit the free agent market (2:48)
